Key Match Events: Cavaliers 105, Nets 100: After trailing by as many as 13 points in the 4th quarter, Evan Mobley (23 pts, 16 reb, 4 stl) and Darius Garland (20 pts, 6 ast) ignited a 16-4 Cavs run to close the game, as Cleveland rallied past Cameron Johnson (23 pts, 5 reb, 4 3s) and the Nets to extend its franchise-best start to 11-0.
